    dc:description "Figs. 1–8. Dorynota (s. str.) species. 1) D. aculeata, paralectotype, dorsal view; 2) D. aculeata, paralectotype, lateral view and labels; 3) D. aurita from Mexico (Durango), dorsal view; 4) D. aurita, lateral view; 5) D. bidens from Brazil (Minas Gerais), dorsal view; 6) D. bidens, lateral view; 7) D. borowieci, holotype, dorsal view; 8) D. borowieci, lateral view." ;
